al registration/cadaster data improvement methodology.  As the IBRD pipeline operation is under preparation, the PLR will provide more detail on the targets and baselines. Increase in percentage of properties registered in the digital registration system gender  Baseline: 10% - 2014 Target: 20% - 2019"
